38
00:02:16.538 --> 00:02:18.120
Show the two together.

39
00:02:20.110 --> 00:02:23.593
In this shot we can
play a little over time,

40
00:02:23.593 --> 00:02:27.625
in the sense of slow
motion in a moment.

41
00:02:27.625 --> 00:02:32.673
Then we will make the
foot appear quickly,

