Here the first
moment can be very fast.

45
00:02:46.093 --> 00:02:49.360
And the slow moment may be
when it is about to gain momentum.

46
00:02:57.145 --> 00:03:01.408
In general I try to use
position and rotation animations.

47
00:03:01.463 --> 00:03:03.662
Thus our object does not deform much,

48
00:03:03.948 --> 00:03:07.038
and we can move it
through space more easily.

49
00:03:08.035 --> 00:03:11.658
Once we have the basic
structure of the movement,

50
00:03:12.075 --> 00:03:15.173
Let's start
adjusting the famous Paths.

