00:03:16.975 --> 00:03:20.465
I will locate the first
keyframes at the moment we define

52
00:03:20.480 --> 00:03:23.280
in our styleframe,
which is this moment.

53
00:03:23.593 --> 00:03:27.610
Here we know that all those keyframes
are fine and we will leave them like this.

54
00:03:27.880 --> 00:03:33.090
Now we are going to start modifying
them to adapt them to each position.

55
00:03:36.548 --> 00:03:39.757
Keep in mind that when
you have a rotated object,

56
00:03:40.078 --> 00:03:43.375
if they use the transformation
box and move it with the keyboard

57
00:03:43.375 --> 00:03:47.278
it will move in the direction
in which the object is rotated.

58
00:03:47.368 --> 00:03:49.343
That can be a bit confusing.

59
00:03:51.000 --> 00:03:54.960
In these cases, perhaps it is
better to simply use the "mouse".

60
00:03:55.400 --> 00:03:56.640
Or the tablet.

