00:04:07.280 --> 00:04:09.953
energy, say, and then boost.

64
00:04:16.418 --> 00:04:19.363
In this moment in which
the foot remains still,

65
00:04:19.363 --> 00:04:22.302
What we will do is make it flex.

66
00:04:22.338 --> 00:04:25.750
When we're more or
less happy with a pose,

67
00:04:25.750 --> 00:04:28.248
we can add keyframes in all Paths,

68
00:04:28.248 --> 00:04:32.718
even those who are not animated yet,
and if we encourage them in the next pose

69
00:04:32.718 --> 00:04:37.133
